main event: Observers in Kaiden, Ohio reported seeing a bright and s-curved object in the sky on 4/7/67.
interesting points: The object was described as bright with varied colors,Several witnesses claimed to see the object moving in an erratic manner,The observers felt the object was not of this world,The encounter lasted for approximately 3 minutes,There is no physical evidence available for this sighting.
witness description: people who saw the bright object in the sky
